---

import { Separator } from '@/components/ui/separator'
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-20 min-h-screen container">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">About Me</h1>
    <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl text-gray-600 leading-7 sm:leading-9">
      Hi there, I'm Kishan. I build modern web products with a focus on
      efficiency, scalability, and emerging AI workflows. I currently work as an
      SDE-2 at Plivo (YC S12), where I ship production-ready AI agents for
      contact centers.
      <br />
      <br />
      At Plivo, I architected and launched AI Studio's Vibe Agent—a self-serve
      automation workspace that lets operations teams design multimodal
      assistants across voice, SMS, and chat. I owned the conversation builder,
      orchestration runtime, channel integrations, and monitoring surface to
      help customers resolve requests faster while meeting enterprise-grade
      reliability expectations.
      <br />
      <br />Previously, at Quinence, I led the redevelopment of Fuschia Careers, a
      high-volume recruiting platform, improving performance, search quality,
      and AI-assisted recruiter workflows. I also architected the Modern
      Fullstack platform end-to-end—spanning the site, backend, and course
      delivery—to unlock a 10× improvement in load times and learner
      engagement.
      <br />
      <br />Before that, I built the backend and smart contracts for The Soulless
      Citadel, a blockchain NFT experience that powered 2,200+ transactions and
      nearly $370,000 in sales. Across every project, I balance a product
      mindset with performance-first engineering, whether that's tuning
      real-time systems, crafting teaching tools, or shaping agentic customer
      journeys.
      <br />
      <br />If you’re interested in collaborating on AI agents or have a project
      in mind, feel free to reach out to me at
      <a
        href="mailto:hello@kishans.in?cc=kishansharma1231@gmail.com&subject=Hey%20Kishan%2C%20we%20have%20some%20exciting%20opportunity%20for%20you"
        class="text-black underline"
      >
        hello@kishans.in.
      </a>
    </p>

    <h2
      class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 sm:mt-10 mb-4 sm:mb-5"
    >
      Experience
    </h2>
    <ul class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/plivo.svg"
          alt="Plivo logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Plivo</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">SDE-2</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">June 2024 → Present</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/quinence.png"
          alt="Quinence logo"
          class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-14 sm:h-14 mb-2 sm:mb-0 sm:mr-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm"
        />
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-semibold">Quinence</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 my-1 mb-2 text-base sm:text-lg">
            Full-Stack Engineer
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-mono">June 2022 → May 2024</p>
        </div>
      </li>
      <Separator className="my-5 sm:my-7" />
      <li class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center">
        <img
          src="assets/logos/increff.png"
          alt="Increff logo"
